## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests (existing suite)

```bash
# From the project root
cd "c:\Users\User\Desktop\UCV\BUSSINES I BIG DATA\REPOSITORIO\Proyecto_ENLA_2026"

# Install deps first if needed
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run only the unit tests (no external connections needed)
pytest tests/unit/ -v

# Run with coverage report
pytest tests/unit/ -v --cov=src --cov-report=term-missing
```

The existing [tests/unit/test_transform.py](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/UCV/BUSSINES%20I%20BIG%20DATA/REPOSITORIO/Proyecto_ENLA_2026/tests/unit/test_transform.py) already covers the ETL transformation logic with mock data. After our fixes, all 30+ tests in that file should pass.

### New Diagnostic Script

I will create `tests/test_ingestion_local.py` — a standalone script that:
1. Creates a minimal synthetic DataFrame mimicking the MINEDU Excel format
2. Runs through [read_excel](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/UCV/BUSSINES%20I%20BIG%20DATA/REPOSITORIO/Proyecto_ENLA_2026/src/ingestion/ingest_enla.py#117-163) → [filter_data](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/UCV/BUSSINES%20I%20BIG%20DATA/REPOSITORIO/Proyecto_ENLA_2026/src/ingestion/ingest_enla.py#164-207) → [validate](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/UCV/BUSSINES%20I%20BIG%20DATA/REPOSITORIO/Proyecto_ENLA_2026/src/ingestion/ingest_enla.py#208-223) → [deduplicate](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/UCV/BUSSINES%20I%20BIG%20DATA/REPOSITORIO/Proyecto_ENLA_2026/src/ingestion/ingest_enla.py#224-242) WITHOUT connecting to MongoDB
3. Prints pass/fail for each step

Run with:
```bash
python tests/test_ingestion_local.py
```

> [!NOTE]
> The full end-to-end integration test (MongoDB + BigQuery) requires real credentials and is run via GitHub Actions.
